    "uen": "198903816N",
    "description": "<p><strong>OUR HERITAGE</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Kingfisher Automotive Pte Ltd,</strong> was established by its founder MR. Gunther Richard Meyer in 1989 under its former name GRM trading Pte Ltd. The company started its trade specializing in commodity trading with special focus on natural rubber for the tyres industry in the early years. The expansion into the domain of components and spares parts supplies for the automotive aftermarket came naturally to a firm already immersed in the industry. The growth in our automotive portfolio eventually reached a stage where it dominates 80% of our entire business. The name Kingfisher Automotive Pte Ltd which has a symbol of peace and prosperity in Greek mythology was then chosen to reflect the changed in its business nature with strong focus on Automotives parts supplies. The company continued to build its portfolio in industrial products by distributing precision laser cutting head from <strong>PRECITEC</strong> and high quality industrial switches from <strong>BERNSTEIN</strong>.</p>\n\n<p><strong>OUR PRODUCTS & SERVICES</strong></p>\n\n<p>Today, we are product distributors for an exclusive selection of the most prominent European Automotive brands such as <strong>WABCO</strong>, <strong>FAG</strong>, <strong>LUK</strong>, <strong>INA</strong>, <strong>FTE</strong>, <strong>HELLA</strong>, <strong>MANN FILTERS</strong>, <strong>ATLAS, OPTI-BELTS and JLM Lubricants</strong>. We also offer quality products and quality service with focused on suspension, chassis, and engine parts. We have partnership with OEM supplier’s which give us access to original Mercedes and MAN parts too. We strive to be a \"one-stop-shop\" partner to our most valuable asset, our customers.</p>\n\n<p>Our industrial portfolio caters to the specific demands of the M&E and Electronic Manufacturing Industries in Singapore and the region. As an exclusive partner for <strong>BERNSTEIN</strong> and <strong>PRECITEC</strong> from Germany, we have a wide range of products available for a myriad of applications.</p>\n",
